title: Killing Off Characters - Killing Off Characters
description:
Killing Off Characters" began as a project to excite one's self away from the sadness of other projects and quickly became among the best things in our lives. Strict music roles have no part here. A musical collective of three thirty-somethings expanding their minds and concepts of musical convention.

Written by Killing Off Characters

Recorded & Produced By David Stephan 
Mixed by David Botrill 
Mastered by Scott Warren
